Main product description: Fan-assisted oven with glass door panel
Catalogue description: The Pro-Lite LD64 is a fan-assisted convection oven with a glass door. Hob units can be mounted upon this appliance.

The Pro-Lite LD203 water boiler is an ideal model to provide continuous boiling water. The boiler has an automatic fill feature, is easy to descale and service and has electronic controls. It has an immediate draw off capacity of 10 litres, with an output of 28 litres per hour or 156 cups.
